Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------SUB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜和我在一起的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时开始像理所当然一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有时候夏娜看上去像个普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至会让我忘记她是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和弗利安格内一战以来的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却一口气把我从这浮夸的心情里拉回了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜是个强大又完美的火雾战士这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槽了槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和昨天一样  感觉杀意躲避攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知  知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么大力打也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不适当的用点力是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢的话快点躲掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还没闭着眼睛锻炼过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然这样肯定不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果感觉杀意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单纯的攻击应该明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像知道对方要出什么的猜拳一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说猜拳什么的前一阵刚玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说得那么了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果输的一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锻炼中别说废话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下啊  搞突然袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击总是很突然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为说了废话才会那么丢脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了等下了  稍微等下也不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人可不会等的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是锻炼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找借口可很难看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是红世之徒的话你已经被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要准备去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  小悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二自作主张结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为锻炼进行得不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢  好像给打得很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前更加不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却摆出一副悠然自得的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许察觉到自己比较差劲了也说不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜是那么可爱又小巧玲珑的女孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打的四脚朝天  作为男孩子来说总有些丢脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我比较强  这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢  男孩子都是爱面子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是在想让她看到优点的女孩子面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常想着悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是对悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放学以后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开封绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微做些动作幅度大的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然做这么夸张的事没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了没问题才锻炼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为男孩子来说总有些丢脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要锻炼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就不丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  算是在鼓励我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是说理所当然的话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说现在相当丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢脸什么的  这种无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是  悠二能变强然后一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有一元硬币的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去小卖部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但大姐恢复原样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会离开这个城市了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我是希望大姐恢复原样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇…！这是一美做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友给了我料理的配方  就想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缘喜欢的话也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和外面卖的完全不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学料理很拿手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是爱好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了  图书管理员在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我和她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是图书馆的书今天要变更排放顺序了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后在图书馆集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为每个班级要派两人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没空的话找个代替的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  要去探望外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家人都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那坂井  你和吉田同学一起去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  不添麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正规定两个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放学以后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开封绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微做些动作幅度大的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和别人说好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  说过要借平井同学的笔记看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同学  下次好了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是我提出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因为是学校的委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上再锻炼也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过今天放学后做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今可说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锻炼才比较重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  但学校也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是我先提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才道歉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要锻炼的不是悠二嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就今天一天有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二太没决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之今天就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有这么任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要参加委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二不锻炼不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为非常弱  非常丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像现在这样完全派不上用处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同学怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  完全没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说只是出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  今天要和坂井一起加班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  小夏娜一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天参加了委员会什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么  那在里面等如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了好吃的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜原来是一个人住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃  千草的也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  回去的时候和坂井独处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一没话题了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  刚才听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2班的平井同学测验全是100分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像体育课上也很厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真有呢  那样的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想问  关于小缘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样总是一个人想下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么看待小缘的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然刚才3班的人也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真是厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  夏娜太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋  真是太没胆子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜都已经吃好饭洗完澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽是我以前的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小夏娜说我想穿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯  挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很晚了就送她回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果知道夏娜晚上住我房间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲会吓一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天份的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  反正已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙始终也只是个无聊的凡人么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红世之徒  对  只要来了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是火雾战士也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要战斗的话  就算是悠二也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磷子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这封绝还真烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？身为悼词朗诵者你不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就是这样了也没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一句话也说不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低谷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好  就交给小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是要悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像错乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是失去主人的磷子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没几天也会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为磷子不管吞食了多少存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不能变成自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了主人的混蛋讨伐工具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可不会被消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我要存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的身体软扑扑的真难砍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消除我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要砍  不要砍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有预定要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为从刚才开始就坐立不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是看外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不去也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为去也派不上用场的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这么说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你自己说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在  存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么吃你都会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那么巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本体的核心却是很小的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在毁掉之前只有不断砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在还没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃的话  存在之力就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说没用的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼  好疼  好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消灭我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消除我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了让小悠派上用场而教你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想只是陪在那个人身边也能帮上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾不周
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想只是陪在那个人身边也能帮上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜就算没有我也能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为夏娜很强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是磷子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  我不想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  住手    住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  要存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  没受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事也习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有点累了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辛苦啊  悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二  变强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的  会变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能让我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真脏啊  别把垃圾乱丢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害  这家伙好有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有钱人家的阔少爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  说说看Help  me什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是  4号第一棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  垃圾虫们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐登场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥这样可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过叫你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好等的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我有好好等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没吃掉这些家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥可真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了哟  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别客气尽管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学会留下火炬的份了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为泰莉亚露说一定要这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高兴  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  兄妹还真干得出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「爱染自」——索拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「爱染他」——泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.11,0:24:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为少女的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.56,0:24:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围绕着她而对峙着的亚拉斯托尔和千草
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.47,0:24:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜所察觉到的「身边的恋情」到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.53,0:24:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  悠二和夏娜和Kiss
